SELECT \n    [Current LSN],\n    [Operation],\n    [Transaction ID],\n    [Login Name],\n    [Database Name],\n    [Schema Name],\n    [Table Name],\n    [Rowsets],\n    [TextData]\nFROM \n    fn_dblog(NULL, NULL)\nWHERE \n    [Operation] IN ('INSERT', 'UPDATE', 'DELETE')\n    AND [Current LSN] > (SELECT [Current LSN] FROM fn_dblog(NULL, NULL) WHERE [Operation] = 'LOP_BEGIN_XACT')\n    AND [Timestamp] > DATEADD(day, -1, GETDATE())\nORDER BY \n    [Timestamp] DESC;